 Kalonzo will be faced with growing discontent within his Wiper Party over nominations for House roles, especially the battle for a slot in the Parliamentary Service Commission (PSC).
 Speaker Justin Muturi ruled that he would wait for a communication from Kalonzo on the party's nominee.
 Kalonzo will also jet back amid plans to swear in Raila Odinga and himself as people’s President and Deputy President.
